content:
Grok Imagine usage is growing by ~50% per day. 

Hyperviral. 

@a and @v growing fast too.

Next week, Grok 3.5 early beta release to SuperGrok subscribers only. 

It is the first AI that can, for example, accurately answer technical questions about rocket engines or electrochemistry.

@Grok is reasoning from first principles and coming up with answers that simply don’t exist on the Internet.

“We are gonna need a bigger compute!”
@xAI
 https://t.co/ckc78vJhL6

I am excited to welcome Linda Yaccarino as the new CEO of Twitter!

@LindaYacc will focus primarily on business operations, while I focus on product design &amp; new technology.

Looking forward to working with Linda to transform this platform into X, the everything app.
